verbose_text: GRPR antagonists ATBBN (D-Phe-Gln-Trp-Ala-Val-Gly-His-Leu-NHCH 2 CH 3) and MATBBN (Gly-Gly-Gly-Arg-Asp-Asn-D-Phe-Gln-Trp-Ala-Val-Gly-His-Leu-NHCH 2 CH 3), and agonists AGBBN (Gln-Trp-Ala-Val-Gly-His-Leu-MetNH 2) and MAGBBN (Gly-Gly-Gly-Arg-Asp-Asn-Gln-Trp-Ala-Val-Gly-His-Leu-MetNH 2) were radiolabeled with 18 F via 4-nitrophenyl 2- 18 F-fluoropropionate.
